    <div id="main">	
	<h1>Aegis Group Search Consultants, LLC</h1>
					<h3>Welcome to Aegis-Group.com</h3>
							<div id="quote">We bring over twenty-eight years of search experience in the healthcare industry.<img src="/images/quote-right.jpg" /></div>
				<p>Aegis Group Search Consultants, LLC is a retained search firm specializing in the recruitment of executives and physician executives for a wide array of sectors in healthcare.</p>
<p>&nbsp;</p>
<p>Examples of the sectors&nbsp;served include Hospitals, Healthcare Systems, Insurer and Managed Care Groups, Physician Organizations, Healthcare Associations, Medical Schools and Pharmaceutical Companies.</p>
<p>&nbsp;</p>
<p>Aegis Group was originally formed in 1991 as a retained executive search firm specializing in the recruitment of Healthcare Executives.&nbsp; In April of 2003 Aegis Group expanded when John Green acquired a majority interest in the firm.&nbsp; The firm&nbsp;was incorporated as Aegis Group Search Consultants, LLC. In June of 2010 John purchased the minority interests of Tim Ignash who retired and took an emeritus status.</p>
<p>&nbsp;</p>
<p>Prior to joining Aegis Group Search Consultants, LLC, the President and CEO, John E. Green, Jr., held healthcare system and hospital administration roles for eight years.</p>
<p>&nbsp;</p>
<p>Aegis Group Search Consultants, LLC is privately owned in order to maximize the focus on&nbsp;efforts to deliver value to our clients rather than to shareholders.</p>
<p>&nbsp;</p>
<p>We are a Minority Business Enterprise certified by the Michigan Minority Business Development Council, the South Central Ohio Minority Business Council, the Northern Ohio Minority Business Council, and the Chicago Minority Business Development Council.</p></div>
